---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body class="bg-white text-slate-900 font-inter">
		<Header />
		<main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 md:py-24">
			<!-- Hero Section -->
			<section class="mb-24">
				<h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-plus-jakarta font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-none mb-8">
					Growth-driven <br />
					<span class="text-accent">Developer</span> SEO
				</h1>
				<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 items-start">
					<div class="md:w-1/2">
						<p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
							이 디지털 정원은 지식이 뿌리를 내리고, 줄기를 뻗으며, 열매를 맺는 과정을 기록합니다.
							단순한 기술 전시를 넘어, 끊임없는 학습과 탐구의 여정을 공유합니다.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="md:w-1/2 relative w-full">
						<!-- Digital Garden Motif (Abstract SVG) -->
						<div class="w-full h-64 md:h-80 bg-gray-extra-light rounded-[32px] border border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
							<svg width="200" height="200" viewBox="0 0 200 200" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="text-accent opacity-20">
								<circle cx="100" cy="100" r="80" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" />
								<path d="M100 20V180M20 100H180" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 4" />
								<circle cx="100" cy="100" r="40" fill="currentColor" class="animate-pulse" />
								<rect x="70" y="70" width="60" height="60" rx="30" stroke="var(--accent-secondary)" stroke-width="2" />
							</svg>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Section Navigation Cards -->
			<section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
				<!-- Tech Research -->
				<a href="/blog" class="group block bg-white border border-slate-100 p-8 rounded-[32px] hover:border-accent transition-all duration-300">
					<div class="mb-12 flex justify-between items-start">
						<span class="font-space-grotesk text-sm text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">01</span>
						<div class="text-slate-300 group-hover:text-accent group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-all duration-300">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" />
							</svg>
						</div>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-3xl font-plus-jakarta font-extrabold mb-4 tracking-tight">Tech Research</h3>
					<p class="text-slate-500 text-lg leading-relaxed">기술에 대한 깊이 있는 조사와 인사이트를 기록하는 잡지 스타일 로그</p>
				</a>

				<!-- Growth Log -->
				<a href="/study" class="group block bg-white border border-slate-100 p-8 rounded-[32px] hover:border-accent-success transition-all duration-300">
					<div class="mb-12 flex justify-between items-start">
						<span class="font-space-grotesk text-sm text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">02</span>
						<div class="text-slate-300 group-hover:text-accent-success group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-all duration-300">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" />
							</svg>
						</div>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-3xl font-plus-jakarta font-extrabold mb-4 tracking-tight">Growth Log</h3>
					<p class="text-slate-500 text-lg leading-relaxed">매일의 배움과 성장을 시계열로 기록하는 타임라인 형식의 학습 정원</p>
				</a>

				<!-- Portfolio -->
				<a href="/portfolio" class="group block bg-white border border-slate-100 p-8 rounded-[32px] hover:border-accent-secondary transition-all duration-300">
					<div class="mb-12 flex justify-between items-start">
						<span class="font-space-grotesk text-sm text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">03</span>
						<div class="text-slate-300 group-hover:text-accent-secondary group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-all duration-300">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" />
							</svg>
						</div>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-3xl font-plus-jakarta font-extrabold mb-4 tracking-tight">Portfolio</h3>
					<p class="text-slate-500 text-lg leading-relaxed">성장의 결과물들이 모여 열매를 맺은 프로젝트 쇼케이스</p>
				</a>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
